      • selectWRTFocusPolicy

        void selectWRTFocusPolicy​(org.jetbrains.mps.openapi.model.SNode node,
                          boolean force)
        Select one of available EditorCells representing passes SNode in the associated editor. If multiple EditorCells are representing same SNode in this editor then most applicable will be selected based on FocusPolicies specified on EditorCells.
        Parameters:
        node - one of EditorCells representing this SNode should be selected
        force - change selection even if getSelectedNode() == node
